description: Toga Limited develops social media app for mobile devices. It offers platforms, products, and services, comprising Yippi, TOGA Resonance Technology (T-RT), TogaGo.com, Games, sticker shop, Eostre, etc. Its online platform provides social messaging app of tourism, trade and transaction, games, technology, and communication software development. The company was formerly known as Blink Couture, Inc. and changed its name to Toga Limited in December 2016. Toga Limited was incorporated in 2003 and is headquartered in Los Angeles, California.
